Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Hello, everyone! Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! And what the heck is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my! They're harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, aren't you a lovely lady?\NMay I please see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Harassment Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! What's up with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he funny? I had him join our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't! I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on inside! Let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not for you to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Revive-Revive Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Revive-Revive Fruit lets you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I'm a revived human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It guarantees the mysterious\Npower of a second shot at life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A revived human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now that I take a closer look,\Nyou don't have a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! What are you, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have spent far too many\Nyears drifting on these seas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to tell my story in one sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G... G-G-G...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! Something's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil be gone! Evil be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's causing that tremor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Be Gone"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how'd an island get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ghost island \Nthat wanders the seas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thriller Bark...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"One Unnatural Phenomenon After the Next!\NDisembarking on Thriller Bark!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec! This isn't\Nshowing up on the Log Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hardly surprising. This island\Ncame clear from the West Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The West Blue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, this is truly my lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only have I run into people, but my\Nheartfelt dream has also come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so agile!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! I became light on my feet\Nafter I died and turned to bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please break through the gate towering\Nover you and escape with all due haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, do not\Ndrop anchor by the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me so very happy to meet you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget that scrumptious meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care! May we have the\Nfortune to meet on other waters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he a power holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why on earth did he jump into the water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's running on the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At any rate, Luffy, let's take his advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on, but this\Nisland is clearly nothing but trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dying to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with this Ghost Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where'd that ghost go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it flew back toward the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably where it resides.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about that large tremor\Nwe felt a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that mouth-like gate \Ncaused it when it shut,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that it essentially devoured us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it ate us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to see through the fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the fence extending from the gate\Nappears to encompass the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, our ship is currently trapped
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inside a fence that surrounds the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! So that's why the skeleton\Ntold us to escape ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean someone is making\Nthis island "wander" the seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the island is moving,\Nwe're still in the middle of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't drop the anchor here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there! Why do I get the\Nfeeling you wanna stay here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta leave now!\NWe're gonna get cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys. I've come down with\NFear-of-unknown-islands-osis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same! I've caught the same bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's take her up to the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have Set-for-Adventure-osis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think that over! Luffy, open up your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that creepy building?!\NIt's a real haunted mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking malicious \Nspirits way too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NI'm being super careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna catch that ghost\Nand keep it as a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally underestimating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And above all else, we have to\Nbring back our dear crewmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, my pirate lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crewmate...? Hey, I'm \Nagainst you on that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be too scared to sleep at night\Nif we had a skeleton for a crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got your lunchbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Franky! You'd better\Nbe sure to protect Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothin' like exploring\Nan uncharted island, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding!\NYou're going with them, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply love the thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! So, guys, we're gonna\Ntake a small boat to disembark,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've still got a special\Nsurprise I haven't shown you yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Soldier Dock System, Channel 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This system uses a total of five channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0 comes up twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each dock has its own unique function.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already revealed the paddle\Nwheel in 0 and the contents in 1 and 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as I recall, you said\N2 and 4 were still empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I was savin' them \Nfor a special occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:10:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone steering clear of the island\Nshould give it a quick spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier Dock System, Channel 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's gonna pop out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With its steam engine, this paddle\Nsteamer that sits four is the Mini-Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry came back as a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's small, but now we can ride Merry again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! I'm getting the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Th-That looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine! You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea he was hiding\Nsuch a wonderful present...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be more than happy to go shopping\Nfor supplies in a boat like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! Gimme a turn! I want a turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took "considerate" to a new level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold your horses, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get to ride it in just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them have a bit of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this everything, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Including the 1 and 3\NI've already shown you, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Channel 0: Support Paddles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Channel 1: The one-man waver,\NWhite Hobby Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Channel 3: The three-man recon\Nsubmarine, Shark Submerge III.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Channel 2: The four-man\Nerrand boat, Mini-Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, this is everything\Nthe Soldier Dock System has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider them soldiers meant to\Nassist the Thousand Sunny's voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love the way you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, you rock! You rock! You rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You rock! You rock! You rock! You rock!\N--Yeah! I'm the ultimate man again this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see squat through this fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her scream came from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, lemme ride the Mini-Merry already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! You should be worried about Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you should be worried about\Nthe other two on top of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that scream means\Na ghost killed them with a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! Don't jinx them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has touched the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too new for the \Ngears to be coming loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, raise it back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to throw the ship off balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did someone touch that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no one went near there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for games!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, vit ishn't me! I'm vot doin' vis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, punk! What was that about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm sorry. My sword sprang out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're not the \Nonly ones on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we've got company, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a ghost after all?\NOr was it some sorta psychic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel someone touching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I heard the sound of a\Nbeast growling just a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm worried about\NNami-san and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you deal with the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna swim to the island\Nand save those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That was lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Sanji's floating back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's he doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "Gah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Why don't you give it a try?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't want us to leave the ship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see what it's after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wanted to kill us, we're wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Robin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has caught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you have your way with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does sound like a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waves are doin' that! Unnatural waves\Nare forming inside the fence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're carrying the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the clear. He seems to have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gah! Raise the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't sail like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling "Gah"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Chopper! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! The current's pulling us\Naway from Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Franky! Use one of the ship's\Nsecret weapons to get us outta this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing! I've got a Peek-a-Boo Vinyl Pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun! Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder that hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fell all the way from up there, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already on Ghost Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me even more scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how in the world did we get down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got too excited over\NMini-Merry and ran ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a bit overconfident, let it rip\Nand rammed into the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when all three of us got sent flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within seconds, we were at\Nthe bottom of this trench.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 100% at fault, but you'll\Nforgive me 'cause I'm cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously gonna whack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:12.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For one thing, isn't it weird\Nhow all this fog appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we entered the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a trap to deal with adversaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should consider ourselves lucky\Nthis wasn't lined with bamboo spears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! We're okay because\Nwe landed on these skeletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've barely set foot on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others will\Ncome for us if we sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm scared of being below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fair enough. It's dangerous and hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, why don't we wait\Nfor help on the shore at ground level?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, like, which way takes us up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? C-Could that be C-Cer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cerberus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Cerberus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's Cerberus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm p-pretty sure it's \Nthe watchdog of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that really exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does! It's right behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we're in Hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't wanna know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just run! It'll eat us if we stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yip"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now that I take a closer look,\Nisn't one of them a fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! That hurt its feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be a sore spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ticked it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's saying, "Pow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must have hit a real sore spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There is a staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will take us to the ground level!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah, it's persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hit a really sore spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dog that doesn't have\Na sense of smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we ran pretty \Ndeep into the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that wandering around, we can't\Nwait somewhere that would stand out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am called Hildon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid you might be in trouble\Nwhen I saw the feral dog chasing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I snuck up from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sneak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As night falls upon the\Nforest around these parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it becomes so perilous it hardly\Nseems like it belongs of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you please, feel free to take\Nmy carriage to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, there is. You're welcome\Nto visit Dr. Hogback's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:23:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hogback...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd get to meet\NDr. Hogback in my wildest dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this Hogback guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's saved as many people\Nas there are stars in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Hey, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.41,0:23:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he's a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.11,0:23:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should get his autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Man Called a Genius!\NHogback Makes His Appearance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
